trans-unit.source: The contract type of the objects in the list.
Represents a generic list of types that are defined by a contract and are used to pass collections of that contract type between a host and an add-in.
trans-unit.target: 계약에 정의된 제네릭 형식 목록을 나타내며, 호스트와 추가 기능 사이에서 해당 계약 형식의 컬렉션을 전달하는 데 사용됩니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.CollectionAdapters> class uses an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> interface to pass collections, in both directions, between the host and the add-in.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.CollectionAdapters> 클래스에서 사용 하는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> 컬렉션, 호스트와 추가 기능 간에 양방향으로 전달 하는 인터페이스입니다.

trans-unit.source: It is recommended that you use the <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.CollectionAdapters> class instead of using this class directly in your code.
trans-unit.target: 사용 하는 것이 좋습니다.는 <xref:System.AddIn.Pipeline.CollectionAdapters> 코드에서 직접이 클래스를 사용 하는 대신 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: For an example, see [Walkthrough: Passing Collections Between Hosts and Add-Ins](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/b532c604-548e-4fab-b11c-377257dd0ee5).
trans-unit.target: 예를 들어 참조 [연습: 호스트 간에 컬렉션 전달 및 추가 기능](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/b532c604-548e-4fab-b11c-377257dd0ee5)합니다.

trans-unit.source: This class can be used to pass objects by reference between application domains because the objects are not serialized.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 개체는 serialize 되지 때문에 응용 프로그램 도메인 간에 개체 참조로 전달 데 사용할 수 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The object to add.
Adds an object to an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
The `item` parameter must be of a type that is defined by the contract.
trans-unit.target: `item` 매개 변수는 서비스 계약에 정의 된 형식 이어야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Removes all objects from an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
The object to look for in the collection.
Determines whether a specific item is in an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
<see langword="true" /> if <paramref name="item" /> is in the collection; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" />가 컬렉션에 있으면 <paramref name="item" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of items in an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
The number of items in the collection.
Returns an enumerator that iterates through an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
An <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IEnumeratorContract`1" /> enumerator to iterate through the collection.
Determines whether an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection is read-only.
<see langword="true" /> if the collection is read-only; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션이 읽기 전용이면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the item to get.
Returns the item at the specified index of an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
The item at the specified index.
The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A> method does not remove the item at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A> 메서드는 지정된 된 인덱스에 항목을 제거 하지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: To remove an item from the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> collection, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 항목을 제거 하는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> 수집, 사용 된 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" />의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: An item in the collection.
Returns the index of a specific item in an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.Collections.IListContract`1" /> 컬렉션에 있는 특정 항목의 인덱스를 반환합니다.

trans-unit.source: The index of the specified item.
If there are several objects of the same type in the collection, this method identifies the index of the item that is the first occurrence of the specified type in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 같은 유형의 여러 개체가 없으면이 메서드는 지정 된 형식의 컬렉션에서 맨 처음 발견 된 항목의 인덱스를 식별 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A> method does not remove the item at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetItem%2A> 메서드는 지정된 된 인덱스에 항목을 제거 하지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: To remove an item from the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> collection, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 항목을 제거 하는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> 수집, 사용 된 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of the <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" /> method.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" /> 메서드의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index at which to insert <c>item</c>.
The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IContract" /> object to insert in the <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
Inserts an item at the specified index in an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
After you call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.Insert%2A> method, the items that follow the insertion point move to accommodate the new item.
trans-unit.target: 호출한 후의 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.Insert%2A> 메서드를 삽입 지점 다음에 오는 항목이 새 항목을 수용 하기 위해 이동 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The indexes of the items that are moved are also updated.
trans-unit.target: 이동 된 항목의 인덱스가 업데이트 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: To replace an item at a specified index, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 지정된 된 인덱스에 항목을 바꾸려면를 사용 하 여는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> collection is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> 컬렉션은 읽기 전용, 호출의 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" />의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection is read-only.
The item to remove from the collection.
Removes an item from an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection of a specified type.
<see langword="true" /> if an item is removed; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: 항목이 제거되었으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: You must repeat this method for each object of a particular type in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션에 특정 종류의 각 개체에 대 한이 메서드를 반복 해야 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The index of the item to remove.
Removes the item at the specified index in an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
After you call <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A>, the items that follow the removed item move to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: 호출한 후 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.RemoveAt%2A>, 제거 된 항목을 아래에 있는 항목 이동 하 여 빈된 자리를 채웁니다.

trans-unit.source: The indexes of the items that are moved are also updated.
trans-unit.target: 이동 된 항목의 인덱스가 업데이트 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: To determine whether an <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> collection is read-only, call the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> 컬렉션은 읽기 전용, 호출의 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="index" /> is less than zero.
-or-
<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of the <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" /> method.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" /> 메서드의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection is read-only.
The zero-based index at which to set the item.
The item to set at the specified index.
Sets the item at the specified index in an <see cref="T:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1" /> collection.
The <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> method sets the item at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.SetItem%2A> 메서드는 지정된 된 인덱스에 항목을 설정 합니다.

trans-unit.source: To add an item to the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> collection, use the <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.Insert%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 항목을 추가 하는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> 수집, 사용 된 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.Insert%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.target: 확인 하려면 여부는 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601> 컬렉션은 읽기 전용, 호출의 <xref:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract%601.GetIsReadOnly%2A> 메서드.

<paramref name="index" /> is equal to or greater than the return value of the <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" /> method.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="index" />가 <see cref="M:System.AddIn.Contract.IListContract`1.GetCount" /> 메서드의 반환 값보다 크거나 같은 경우
